dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Includes table : Administrativno - territorial'noe ustroĭstvo administrativnykh raĭonov [listing and locating territorial administrative divisions.] Воронежская область. Администартивно-территориальное устройство административных районов. Verso: index, statistical data tables, key to abbreviations. Publisher's map no.: V-2614. В-2614 Map shows administrative boundaries, roads, railroads and bridges.
